    <p>In­dulge in an a la carte buf­fet with 50 dishes from $30.80++ at Ban Heng Group of Restau­rants, where one adult dines free for ev­ery three pay­ing adults. For more food op­tions, con­sider its Buf­fet B Menu that in­cludes Bud­dha Jumps</p>
    <p>Over The Wall and chilli crab. Re­fer to www.ban­heng.com.sg for the full menu and prices.</p>
    <p>Plan­ning a small wed­ding lunch or dinner party? Func­tion rooms can be booked for a max­i­mum of 100 peo­ple. Prices are $858 nett for 10 peo­ple and $429 nett for a ta­ble of five peo­ple.</p>
    <p>Make a reser­va­tion on­line or call Aranda Coun­try Club (6585-1770), Boon Keng (6291-0407), Har­bourfront (6278-0288), Or­chard Cen­tral (6238-1516) or Or­chid</p>
    <p>Coun­try Club (6732-7888).</p>


